{"tid":1560745,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"香港政府想同大陸買更多電 <公眾咨詢到7月20日!!>","createTime":"2019-09-11T10:31:00.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T16:10:57.000Z","uid":299161,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"96d7d5446e0a57cce953495892fd1e8efb04b59c","tid":1560745,"uid":299161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T10:31:00.000Z","msg":"政府正建議要向內地買更多電, 其中包括核電! 表面上話係為左減排，實際上可能係政治原因，被迫用香港公帑去幫大陸內地經濟填債，陰乾香港儲備。大家快D去表達意見! !<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>公眾咨詢到9月20號, 仲有10日!!</strong></span></span><br />\n諮詢文件:  <a href=\"https://www.susdev.org.hk/download/pe_document_c.pdf\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.susdev.org.hk%2Fdownload%2Fpe_document_c.pdf&d=33lQL0pOg%2F%2Bbj%2F%2FH3PrIWYOqxcwteoRdaW8BGlJRIvY%3D&h=87c199fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.susdev.org.hk/download/pe_document_c.pdf</a><br />\n<br />\n參考左唔同網上資料同另一個Post (<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1458471/page/1?post=2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1458471/page/1?post=2</a>), 我Draft左以下Template。最好改一改先SEND，以免話係重複意見~<br />\n<br />\n另外，唔建議填網頁入面嘅問卷。因為D問題好空範，又冇實際方案俾人揀，政府可以隨意解讀同演繹市民意見。<br />\n<br />\n電郵: comments@susdev.org.hk<br />\n<br />\n可持續發展委員會委員:<br />\n就《長遠減碳策略公眾參與》，本人反對增加向內地購買電力，原因如下: <em><span style=\"color: blue;\">(按需要選擇不同項目)</span></em><br />\n1) 電力價格將由內地決定。即使價格高昂，但由於本港對內地電力供應的依賴，香港政府只能無奈接受 ，不能反對 (以東江水為例)。<br />\n2) 令香港的公用事業 (水, 電) 對內地愈來愈倚賴，架空香港各方面的自主性。<br />\n3) 核電安全性成疑，萬一發生重大輻射洩漏事故，將嚴重污染環境及危害人體健康，風險極高。香港作為負責任的國際城市，不應明知核電的危害仍故意參與製造另一場環境危機。<br />\n4) 核電比碳排放影響更深遠，以環保角度而言，不應單單為減碳而增加本就受爭議的核電比例，否則只係為跑數而跑數，而非真正為環保。<br />\n5) 內地本身對電力需求都很大，亦經常停電，穩定度遠遠低於香港要求，供電的可靠性成疑。<br />\n6) 現在中電同港燈都計劃增加天然氣比例，另外亦有不同計劃增加可再生能源比例，例如太陽能發電場、浮動太陽能板發電系統、水力發電站、污泥焚化、綜合廢物管理設施焚化發電、上網電價計劃等等。政府應積極發展及擴大上述項目，增加可再生能源比例，令香港供電能夠自給自足。<br />\n一名香港市民上"},{"pid":"895381f4cfa8c982e411d9aafb92848bd8d6c23a","tid":1560745,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T10:31:55.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />出黎呀 自由閪！ <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></div></strong></span></span><br />\n<strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"> <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />五大訴求 缺一不可 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></div></strong><br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/aPJ3iwW.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FaPJ3iwW.png&h=bd74ec1d&s={SIZE}\" /></div>"},{"pid":"6dca18d1d41d223344ec3f7d11c6c39bc001373f","tid":1560745,"uid":43428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T10:34:10.000Z","msg":"好地地走去買電 買完電又會話香港依賴大陸 <br />\n呢個咁無恥既劇本已經睇到"},{"pid":"1e457fd5b56175d7924bf3030856f4bae182f13f","tid":1560745,"uid":2445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T10:35:23.000Z","msg":"你打左7月20日喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5482a149570f3d1af38ec113a8552bf1ffa0ce38","tid":1560745,"uid":299161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e457fd5b56175d7924bf3030856f4bae182f13f","tid":1560745,"uid":2445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T10:35:23.000Z","msg":"你打左7月20日喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T10:36:26.000Z","msg":"手快打錯左.."},{"pid":"4eeb94661c11d14d15d1cddba3978328951c0d6e","tid":1560745,"uid":299161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1e457fd5b56175d7924bf3030856f4bae182f13f","tid":1560745,"uid":2445,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T10:35:23.000Z","msg":"你打左7月20日喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T10:39:14.000Z","msg":"P牌冇得出過"},{"pid":"bd808b66fa11cb4ae466473394a873ececcf11fc","tid":1560745,"uid":3149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T10:40:02.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e178880d3d883976025bba65736d867214c43fa5","tid":1560745,"uid":265221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-11T16:10:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GVZmYc0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGVZmYc0.jpg&h=308b2b89&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Hyxr9jF.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHyxr9jF.jpg&h=2c6e5ee9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n★✰★✰★非常緊急★✰★✰★<br />\n林鄭又再賣港<br />\n政府死心不息，要向中國買電利益輸送，<br />\n今次用減排既名義買電，唔想好似澳門同大陸咁大停電<br />\n記得9月20日號之前<br />\n電郵去 comments@susdev.org.hk<br />\n反對向中國買電﹗﹗<br />\n<br />\n參考意見：<br />\n1 .反對更緊密的區域合作，應以香港本地發電為主，以便港府監管，確保電力穩定；<br />\n2.跟從2014年未來發電燃料組合諮詢結果，增加本地可再生能源及天然氣發電比例；<br />\n3 .爭取香港以小島嶼發展中國家/地區(small island developing states) 名義，以更彈性的方式履行《巴黎協定》；<br />\n4 .放緩人口增長，如減少單程證、優才計劃等，減低整體電力消耗；<br />\n5 .加強本地農業、製造業及回收等行業，減少運輸所造成的碳排放。"}]}